OL,3,CParents seek legal action over SEN
OL,4,Cschool places
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation has revealed
OL,7,Fthe true scale of the crisis in
OL,8,Fspecial educational needs provision
OL,9,Facross Northern Ireland, England and
OL,10,FWales.
OL,12,FITV News is shining a spotlight on
OL,13,FSEND - or SEN as it's referred to in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,16,FParents here say they are having to
OL,17,Ftake legal action because they can't
OL,18,Fget their children into a school which
OL,19,Fmeets their specific needs because
OL,20,Fthere are no places.
