OL,4,Cschool places
OL,6,FKaren Marshall's son and Nicole
OL,7,FMcKenna's son have special educational
OL,8,Fneeds and just over a month to the
OL,9,Fstart of the new school year, neither
OL,10,Fboy has a primary school place.
OL,12,FKaren told UTV: " You're just
OL,13,Fconstantly waiting for that phone call
OL,14,Fand constantly chasing. It just feels
OL,15,Flike they are at the bottom of
OL,16,Fsomeone's list, in terms of our next
OL,17,Fstep, it is disgusting that it has got
OL,18,Fto this point, but we're having to go
OL,19,Fdown the legal route."
