OL,6,FNicole told UTV: " You're constantly
OL,7,Fwaiting on the phone ringing to get
OL,8,Fsome good news or trying to contact
OL,9,Fthe Education Authority to get an
OL,10,Fupdate you're being palmed off to
OL,11,Feverybody, you're getting different
OL,12,Femail addresses, different phone
OL,13,Fnumbers, different names.
OL,15,F"You're being told they're off,
OL,16,Fthey're off on leave, so basically
OL,17,Fwait until school starts to find out
OL,18,Fwhether or not there is going to any
OL,19,Fplaces left for your child, it's just
OL,20,Fnot on."
