OL,6,FNorthern Ireland Commissioner for
OL,7,FChildren and Young People Chris Quinn
OL,8,Fsaid:" We need systemic change, we
OL,9,Fneed to get out of this cycle of year
OL,10,Fon year placement crisis, our children
OL,11,Fand our young people and their parents
OL,12,Fdeserve better."
OL,14,FA study published by a group which
OL,15,Frepresents children with special
OL,16,Feducational needs shows that Nicole
OL,17,Fand Karen's experiences are not unique.
OL,19,FAccording to statistics from the SEN
OL,20,FReform Report NI:
