OL,6,FIn a statement the Education Authority
OL,7,Fsaid:" Transformation of the existing
OL,8,Fspecial educational needs system is a
OL,9,Fkey priority for the Education
OL,10,FAuthority."
OL,12,F"We are also committed to ensuring all
OL,13,Fchildren and young people with a
OL,14,Fstatement of SEN receive a placement
OL,15,Fwhich meets their individual needs and
OL,16,Fenables them to reach their full
OL,17,Fpotential."
